{"tid":2195599,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大女生藏六角匙索帶被控 《鏗鏘集》編導潘達培出庭證工具與課堂有關","createTime":"2020-09-09T09:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T16:27:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"753df1d13e1794b4d5635c67a98bb87ec059fbd9","tid":2195599,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:27:43.000Z","msg":"去年11月11日網民號召「大三罷」，各處均有示威者阻路事件。21歲女大學生在牛頭角觀塘道遭防暴警追截，搜獲一包袋口密封的六角匙及一包索帶，女生否認一項管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途使用罪，案件今在觀塘裁判法院開審。兩警作供時均指，現場看不見有人設路障，惟其中一人稱：「根據現場環境裝束及打扮，我相信（她）曾經參與」。而被告的畢業作品指導導師、港台《鏗鏘集》編導潘達培則出庭力證，指涉案工具與其準備畢業作品有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/2FNVWXT4QJBTZFBSJZHTGY4B7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2F2FNVWXT4QJBTZFBSJZHTGY4B7Q%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg2%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=49288bf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2F2FNVWXT4QJBTZFBSJZHTGY4B7Q%2F&h=22b441cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/2FNVWXT4QJBTZFBSJZHTGY4B7Q/</a>"},{"pid":"67914677cb0b023abec3862cc7692e0b9a5b642a","tid":2195599,"uid":124180,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:30:29.000Z","msg":"市民都係憑打扮分到邊類人係社會垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d934f37b1e0c30b887552f7840ad9fe811f66f03","tid":2195599,"uid":194298,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:32:25.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都要上庭搞一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過律政檢控同黑警依然係無成本無後果"},{"pid":"059f06e303438965ec2ecd3e7056f269ab296eec","tid":2195599,"uid":151313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:38:44.000Z","msg":"我有理由相信班黑警係殺人兇手"},{"pid":"73e601bc3e84ef8a0986a749b8e6936d2d0ffab5","tid":2195599,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"059f06e303438965ec2ecd3e7056f269ab2